Subtitle of House Bill 1075
TO PROHIBIT A LOCAL GOVERNMENT FROM REGULATING THE SALE OR USE OF A
LAWN CARE DEVICE OR IMPOSING A TAX OR FEE ON THE USE OF A LAWN CARE
DEVICE IN CERTAIN CIRCUMSTANCES.
____________________________________________________________
